{"tid":2120233,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"★英國公布BNO持有人明年起申請5年居留新安排","createTime":"2020-07-22T14:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T03:02:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3bc4ec0918c2008160302da157404e3e8bc07205","tid":2120233,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"英國政府在網頁公布，申請人可以由明年一月起，申請在英國先逗留30個月、再續期30個月；又或者最長一次過居留5年，期間可以工作或讀書，以及可攜同家屬一同前往英國，但不可領取社會福利及援助。在居留5年後12個月，申請人就可以申請入籍。<br />\n<br />\n申請人須擁有BNO的身份，並不需要現時持有有效BNO護照。條文又要求申請人通常居住在香港、以及有至少6個月的財務支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539312-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539312-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=2a4d1cd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539312-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=971a55a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539312-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"26ce0efc906e3c3ca91b83ee871272b15cf15b35","tid":2120233,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"唔駛曬錢續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3d33d9882d1c2eef30f1fde4137a82d44a59e8","tid":2120233,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff62aab29060b41fe9d00c3abfa31baa34195844","tid":2120233,"uid":326526,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"今日一次過太多消息啦<br />\n班打手點消化得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk